<HEAD>Lucas Working at Justice</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Even before he has been formally approved, the
controversial nominee to head the Bush administration's civil
rights program is working at the Justice Department.
   William Lucas is working as a $284-a-day consultant while
